614
00:45:48,220 --> 00:45:49,480
I told you I didn't foul!

615
00:45:49,480 --> 00:45:50,690
Didn't you hear?

616
00:45:56,410 --> 00:45:57,040
Zhang Yixiang.

617
00:45:58,300 --> 00:45:59,220
Zhang Yixiang.

618
00:46:01,990 --> 00:46:03,420
You better watch that attitude.

