00:46:07,750 --> 00:46:09,640
I despise you.

620
00:46:09,640 --> 00:46:10,520
So what?

621
00:46:15,850 --> 00:46:17,870
Talk all you want but mind your manners.

622
00:46:18,250 --> 00:46:19,550
