632
00:47:04,820 --> 00:47:05,580
Zhang Yixiang!

633
00:47:05,580 --> 00:47:06,590
Get off me.

634
00:47:07,590 --> 00:47:08,690
Zhang Yixiang!

635
00:47:08,690 --> 00:47:09,610
What?

636
00:47:39,390 --> 00:47:40,310
How could

637
00:47:40,310 --> 00:47:41,780
