659
00:49:53,320 --> 00:49:55,040
I'll go to Australia, get a part-time job and save up money.

660
00:49:55,800 --> 00:49:58,240
In college, I will work-study

661
00:49:59,200 --> 00:50:00,920
and save one million in four years.

662
00:50:00,920 --> 00:50:02,350
Then, we'll get married.

663
00:50:04,330 --> 00:50:06,300
You don't have to worry about our living expenses.

664
00:50:07,560 --> 00:50:09,410
Just keep doing what you want to do.

665
00:50:10,790 --> 00:50:12,680
Let me handle the rest.

666
00:50:14,240 --> 00:50:15,580
I want to be with you all the time.

667
00:50:33,680 --> 00:50:34,350
With your mother's connections,

668
00:50:34,350 --> 00:50:36,240
