669
00:50:37,420 --> 00:50:39,180
I'll leave here after you graduate.

670
00:50:40,190 --> 00:50:41,540
You don't need to save up for me,

671
00:50:41,960 --> 00:50:43,510
because I won't be

672
00:50:43,510 --> 00:50:44,900
your kept woman.

673
00:50:45,740 --> 00:50:47,000
Let's go our separate ways

674
00:50:47,540 --> 00:50:48,760
and spare each other.

675
00:50:51,030 --> 00:50:52,250
What do you mean?

676
00:50:53,670 --> 00:50:54,810
You know what I mean.

677
00:50:56,610 --> 00:50:57,870
Is it because of Li Dawei?

678
00:51:00,860 --> 00:51:02,790
I said, is it because of Li Dawei?

679
00:51:04,850 --> 00:51:05,430
Answer me.

680
00:51:05,430 --> 00:51:07,200
On that day you two had dinner at your grandma's,

681
00:51:07,200 --> 00:51:09,090
Nothing else happened?

