690
00:51:25,550 --> 00:51:26,810
How long can I afford to wait?

691
00:51:26,810 --> 00:51:28,240
Then let's get married now.

692
00:51:28,530 --> 00:51:30,720
Anyway, I'm 18. I don't have to ask anyone.

693
00:51:30,720 --> 00:51:31,640
Let's do it now.

694
00:51:32,360 --> 00:51:33,740
Are you kidding me?

695
00:51:36,510 --> 00:51:38,070
I don't want to waste any more time.

696
00:51:38,490 --> 00:51:39,240
We have to break up.

697
00:51:40,540 --> 00:51:41,680
Break up?

698
00:51:42,770 --> 00:51:44,660
Didn't you say sleeping together doesn't mean a thing?

699
00:51:46,170 --> 00:51:47,100
Miss Chen,

700
00:51:47,730 --> 00:51:50,080
